🤖 **Common Retrofit mistakes and fixes.**

| Mistake | Fix |
|---------|-----|
| Not suspend | Use `suspend fun` |
| Wrong method | Use correct annotation |
| No error handling | Use `try-catch` |
| No loading state | Add loading state |

**Fixes:**
```kotlin
